    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The behavior I describe has been around for a while so I think it's independent of #769.\n\ndoing `ls` in a directory with a unicode file worked as of 56d2d8de76d8f1374c8858261097813d5e5ee5b0 on Aug 18th, and broke\nin adba85c00016d40383a5991854916c63b2ecc03f on the next day(which is why I requested that @epatters take a look).\n"
  },
