    "created_at": "2011-09-07T20:24:50Z",
    "updated_at": "2011-09-07T20:24:50Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@ivanov, this is not Windows-specific. As noted in my comments, the Qt console can deadlock when run as a background process. This happens _every time_ for me under OS X (and has been reported by several others). It may be safe for certain Linux configurations, but it is not safe in general.\n\nI can experiment under Linux, but surely there is a better solution for Unicode support than this?\n"
  },
